  "texts": [
    "For segmentation, the DECIMER-Segmentation model 23 was used.",
    "It uses Mask-RCNN 40 to predict an initial mask for each chemical structure in a PDF page and a deterministic mask expansion algorithm to refine the initial masks.",
    "The mask expansion algorithm was optimized and multi-processed to allow large-scale processing.",
    "The model was trained on pages of patent documents to improve its precision and recall for this application domain.",
    "For further details, we refer to publication 23."
  ],
